                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The regiment draws or reloads their crossbows and concentrates fire on creatures in a @Template[type:burst|distance:10] within 60 feet that deals @Damage[4d8[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage (@Check[reflex|dc:26|basic] save). When the regiment is reduced to 2 segments, this area decreases to a @Template[type:burst|distance:5].</p>"
