                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The regiment strikes with their longswords against enemies in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5] (@Check[reflex|dc:26|basic] save). Damage dealt depends on the number of actions. If a creature critically fails the Reflex save while affected by the regiment's Denounce Divinity, it is unable to reduce its stupefied or frightened condition by any means for 1 round.</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[(1d8+2)[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(2d8+11)[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(3d8+13)[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>"
